<div class="faq-section">
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 class="faq-question">When should we book for a 2026-2027 wedding?</h3>
    <p class="faq-answer">For 2027 weddings, now through mid-2026 is optimal. For remaining 2026 dates (autumn/shoulder season), book immediately as availability is limited. Peak season dates book 12-18 months in advance—2027 dates have excellent availability, while late 2026 and shoulder seasons still have options.</p>
